3 thank you car !	you are welcome my driver !

3 for the whole week , please !	the weather next_few_days for oakland is going to be a series of ups and downs from drizzle on sunday to a overcast on thursday and to overcast on friday the highs are forecast to be near 100f with lows near 20f
4 thank you so much for the information	you are welcome have a good day
